<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= link_to (image_tag ('/assets/artcaring.png')), root_path, class: "navbar-brand" %>
    <br>
    Hello <%= @artwork.user.first_name %>,

    Congratulations!

    <%= @buyer.name %> has just purchased <%= @artwork.title %>, here on ArtCaring.com, through your Patient Campaign for <@artwork.user.patient_campaign.full_name %>!
    <br> 

    Please ship it to:

    <%= @buyer.shipping_name %>
    <%= @buyer.shipping_address_line_1 %>
    <% if @buyer.shipping_address_apartment %>
      <%= @buyer.shipping_address_apartment %>
    <% end %>
    <%= @buyer.shipping_address_city %>, <%= @buyer.shipping_address_state %>
    <%= @buyer.shipping_address_zip %>
    <%= @buyer.shipping_address_country_code %>
    <br>
    <br>
    Buyer's email: <%=@buyer.email %>

    <p>Please contact the buyer through this email address to notify them that their purchase has shipped, and provide tracking information to them.</p>

    <hr>

    <p><strong>*It is your responsibility to professionally crate/package this Artwork for shipment, and to make sure it has insurance in transit to the buyer.</strong>

    <hr>

    <p>After the buyer has received and unpacked this purchase, they have 5 business days to either finalize their purchase by keeping the shipment, return it for a refund, or notify us in the case of any damage claims. Buyers are responsible for the cost of any return shipment to you, the artist, and are required to insure the return shipment while in transit.</p> 
    <hr>

    <p>Once the buyer has finalized their purchase, distributions of the appropriate funds will be sent to your Patient's account and to your account if you opted to keep a portion of your Campaign's sales.</p>

    <strong>Thank you, again, for being a part of ArtCaring!</strong>
  </body>
</html>